    <title>Refugees contributor: Imran Mohammad</title>
    <description>Imran Mohammad is a Rohingya refugee who has been held in Australia’s offshore detention center on Papua New Guinea’s Manus Island since 2013. He learned English in detention and now writes for the Australian student newspaper Honi Soit.
